              ->  Table Scan on mysql_compat_index_hint.t [ForceOneCN]  𝄀
                    Filter Cond: (t.b = 7), t.a in ([g01 g03 g05])  𝄀
                    Runtime Filter Probe: t.id  𝄀
              ->  Index Table Scan on t.idx_b_a_id [ForceOneCN]  𝄀
                    Filter Cond: prefix_eq(__mo_index_idx_col), serial_extract(__mo_index_idx_col, 1, VARCHAR)) in ([g01 g03 g05])
